      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>ketchup</strong> and <strong>mustard ketchup</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>special sauce</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche buns </strong>in half</p><p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled</strong> <strong>cucumber wedges </strong>and discard the liquid</p>",
