    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free patties have cooked through, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the<strong> brioche halves</strong> to the other side of the tray</p><p>Top the meat-free patties with the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and return the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>to the oven for 3-4 min or until the brioche buns are warmed through and the cheese has melted – these are your<strong> cheesy veggie patties</strong></p>",
