    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, spread the <strong>special sauce</strong> onto each <strong>warmed brioche base</strong>, then top with a<strong> cheesy veggie patty</strong>, a sprinkling of <strong>crispy onions</strong> and a <strong>warmed brioche lid</strong> – these are your <strong>American-style veggie cheeseburgers</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>potato wedges </strong>and<strong> quick-pickled cucumber wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
